        dc:description           "FIGURE 17. A–B: Galaxias longifundus sp. nov. holotype, NMV A.30575-2, 81.0 mm LCF, Rintoul Creek, C12 Track, north of Tyers, Victoria, A) line drawing (R. Plant), B) image of preserved specimen (note: tail curved slightly to the left in horizontal plane) (T.A. Raadik); C) G. longifundus sp. nov., female, 65 mm LCF, collected at the type locality, 30 April 2012 (T.A. Raadik); D) Rintoul Creek, at type locality of G. longifundus sp. nov., 30 April 2012 (T.A. Raadik). Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
